643
00:54:01,720 --> 00:54:08,400
And then I think we just give women weird advice. 
Here's a hot take. I think we tell women things  

644
00:54:08,400 --> 00:54:13,560
like, you need to find a mentor and you need to 
find a sponsor, and that's just another set of  

645
00:54:13,560 --> 00:54:20,120
hoops that we have that we tell women to jump 
through that I don't think we tell other parts  

646
00:54:20,120 --> 00:54:26,760
of the population to jump through. I think we tell 
women to unlock your future success, you've got to  

647
00:54:26,760 --> 00:54:31,840
find somebody who has made all the same life 
