655
00:55:09,760 --> 00:55:12,040
Thank you for sharing all that. I wasn't 
planning on going in this direction,  

656
00:55:12,040 --> 00:55:17,360
but this is such important advice for say, young 
women that are just getting started in the same  

657
00:55:17,360 --> 00:55:23,840
product. Is there any advice you'd want to 
share to help them get to be the next Ami?

658
00:55:23,840 --> 00:55:29,360
Oh, I mean number one, no next Ami, they're going 
to be their next themselves. That is maybe the  

