661
00:55:42,760 --> 00:55:45,920
just continue expanding. 
Whenever you run into a problem,  

662
00:55:45,920 --> 00:55:50,080
just add more to the things that you can 
do, the tools that you have, the way you  

663
00:55:50,080 --> 00:55:56,240
can express yourself. Just keep on adding 
