01:12:49,280 --> 01:12:54,520
At temp, okay, amazing. And then you ended 
up leading Facebook ads and then WhatsApp  

867
01:12:54,520 --> 01:12:59,320
and many other things. Can you share that story 
of just how you joined and how that happened?

868
01:12:59,320 --> 01:13:09,440
Well, I had quit my last job. I knew that what I 
wanted to do was be involved in all the wild stuff  

869
01:13:09,440 --> 01:13:17,840
happening in Silicon Valley in the mid 2000s. So 
I'd quit my last job, I was traveling around the  

870
01:13:17,840 --> 01:13:25,280
world a little bit. I was living in New York, an 
extremely blissful lifestyle. I was unemployed,  

871
01:13:25,280 --> 01:13:28,800
I was doing whatever I wanted. It was 
some of the best time I've had in my life,  

872
01:13:28,800 --> 01:13:35,400
and eventually I needed a job, like you do. But 
it was 2007 and the only place I wanted to work  

873
01:13:35,400 --> 01:13:42,920
was Facebook. You could hear the way people 
talked about these products. People would say  

874
01:13:42,920 --> 01:13:49,480
Facebook is more important than than my car. It's 
